flowchart TB
    S1["1. create data directory"]
    S2["2. run migrations to current version<br/>(paramodel-store first, then<br/>hyperplane-store; consistency check)"]
    S3["3. mint system API key<br/>→ credentials/system-api-key (0600)"]
    S4["4. prompt for initial admin user<br/>→ username + password in users table"]
    S5["5. mint bootstrap admin token (24h)<br/>→ print to stdout for hyper login"]
    S6["6. emit SYSTEM_INITIALIZED event<br/>exit 0"]

    S1 --> S2 --> S3 --> S4 --> S5 --> S6

    Note["re-running on an initialised install →<br/>AlreadyInitialized<br/>(destructive re-init requires<br/>deleting data directory first)"]
    S6 -.-> Note

    classDef step fill:#e8f0ff,stroke:#3366aa
    classDef note fill:#f0f0f0,stroke:#666
    class S1,S2,S3,S4,S5,S6 step
    class Note note
